@startuml Activity-Template
!define SWIMLANE partition

title [Process Name] Process - Activity Diagram

|#LightBlue|User|
start
:Start process;

|#LightGreen|System|
:Validate input;

if (Input valid?) then (yes)
  :Process request;
  
  |#LightYellow|Database|
  :Save data;
  
  |#LightGreen|System|
  :Generate response;
  
else (no)
  :Show error;
  
  |#LightBlue|User|
  :Correct input;
  stop
endif

|#LightBlue|User|
:Receive confirmation;

' Parallel process (optional)
fork
  :Send email notification;
fork again
  :Update system log;
end fork

stop

note right
  Swimlanes represent
  the different actors/systems
  involved in the process
end note

@enduml
